3567&page=98|title=GrEAT BULAGA @ 28: 2007 - Post #1949|date=July 13, 2007|publisher=PinoyExchange|access-date=September 29, 2016}}</ref>\n*Millet Advincula (1990s)<ref name=\"PinoyExchange\"/>\n*[[Mitoy Yonting]] (1997, 2006\u20132009)\n*[[Mr. Fu]] (2009)\n*Music Hero Band (2016\u20132019)\n*Nadine Schmidt (2002)\n*Nicole Hyala (2015\u20132016)\n*[[Ni\u00f1o Muhlach]] (early 1990s)<ref name=\"pinoyexchange.com\">{{cite web |url=http://www.pinoyexchange.com/forums/showthread.php?t=132169&page=12|title=Eat Bulaga's 25 years celebration - Post #225|date=March 10, 2004|publisher=PinoyExchange|access-date=September 29, 2016}}</ref>\n*[[Nova Villa]] (1989\u20131995)\n*OctoArts Dancers (1989\u20131992)\n*[[Ogie Alcasid]] (1988\u20131989)\n*[[Onemig Bondoc]] (1996\u20131997)\n*Patani Da\u00f1o (2008)\n*[[Patricia Fernandez (actress)|Patricia Fernandez]] (2010, official photographer, ''Bolagaan'' segment)\n*[[Patricia Tumulak]] (2015\u20132017)\n*[[Pepe Pimentel]] (1980s)<ref>{{cite web |url=http://filmacademyphil.org/?p=1532|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201182306/http://filmacademyphil.org/?p=1532|url-status=dead|archive-date=December 1, 2017|title=NOONTIME TV SHOWS|date=July 21, 2009|publisher=Film Academy of the Philippines|last1=Clarin|first1=Tess|access-date=November 21, 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Phoemela Baranda|Phoemela Barranda]] (2001\u20132002)\n*Plinky Recto (1989\u20131992)\n*[[Pops Fernandez]] (1987\u20131988)\n*Priscilla Monteyro (2009\u20132010) \n*The Quandos (2015\u20132016)\n*Rachel Ann Wolf<ref name=\"Eat Bulaga and Beauty Queens\"/>\n*Rading Carlos\u2020 (1980s)<ref name=\"PinoyExchange\"/>\n*[[Randy Santiago]] (1995)<ref name=\"pinoyexchange.com\"/>\n*Rannie Raymundo (1993)\n*Raqi Terra (2018\u20132019)\n*Rey de la Cruz (1980s)<ref name=\"PinoyExchange\"/>\n*Rey Pumaloy (1995\u20132000, ''Aminin'' segment)\n*[[Richard Hwan]] (2014\u20132015)\n*Richard Merk<ref name=\"eb25pinoyexchangepage43\">{{cite web |url=https://www.pinoyexchange.com/discussi